<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.7">
<l>kalaṅka mākkaṭal kaṭaintaṭait tilaṅkaiyar kōṉatu varaiyākam</l>
<l>malaṅka veñcamat taṭucaran turantavem maṭikaḷum vārāṉāl</l>
<l>ilaṅku veṅkati riḷamati yataṉoṭum viṭaimaṇi yaṭumāyaṉ</l>
<l>vilaṅkal vēyiṉa tōcaiyu māyiṉi viḷaivatoṉ ṟaṟiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our lord who, having churned the great sea so that it tossed</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] having dammed it, sent destructive arrows in heated battle,</l>
<l>So that the mountain chest of the king of those of Laṅkā trembled,</l>
<l rend="indent">he does not come [here] at all!</l>
<l>The glowing hot rays of the new moon and the bull bells destroy [me].</l>
<l>The sound of the herder’s mountain bamboo [flute] is anguish, too.</l>
<l rend="indent">I do not know what will happen now.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
